022import java.util.Locale;
023
024import org.apiguardian.api.API;
025import org.tquadrat.foundation.annotation.ClassVersion;

027/**
028 *  Entries for resource bundle properties files.
029 *
030 *  @extauthor Thomas Thrien - thomas.thrien@tquadrat.org
031 *  @version $Id: TextEntry.java 880 2021-02-27 10:47:40Z tquadrat $
032 *  @since 0.1.0
033 *
034 *  @param  key The resource bundle key for the text or message.
035 *  @param  isMessage   {@code true} if the entry is for a message,
036 *      {@code false} if not.
037 *  @param  locale  The locale for this translation of a text or a message.
038 *  @param  description The description for the text or message.
039 *  @param  text    The text or message itself for the given locale.
040 *  @param  className   The fully qualified name of the class that defines
041 *      the text or message.
042 *
043 *  @UMLGraph.link
044 */
045@ClassVersion( sourceVersion = "$Id: TextEntry.java 880 2021-02-27 10:47:40Z tquadrat $" )
046@API( status = INTERNAL, since = "0.1.0" )
047public record TextEntry( String key, boolean isMessage, Locale locale, String description, String text, String className )
048{ /* Empty */ }
